com.facebook.react

Class ReactNativeCorePackage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.react.LazyReactPackage
      • com.facebook.react.ReactNativeCorePackage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReactPackage

    public class ReactNativeCorePackage
extends LazyReactPackage
    Package defining core framework modules for initializing ReactNative (e.g. UIManager). It should be used for modules that require special integration with other framework parts (e.g. with the list of packages to load view managers from).
